{"type": "article", "id": 6860, "title": "Logitech 便携式摄像头", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-27T07:48:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135625N5L74A3VIjBuKwSd.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tLogitech 做了一款便携式的会议摄像头，这款摄像头拥有 90 度的视角和 360 度收声，支持高清视频录制。内置装有可充电电池，采用 NFC 和蓝牙连接方式。外表有黑色和红色颜色可选。可以拆卸的底座和遥控器增加了摄像头的便携性。对于小团体的会议非常方便。目前市场定价为 500 美元。（约合 3130 元人民币）\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135623OsrvKXwGecQnCWVd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"1.37166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061356242vzeNuiKZsqQ5wEh.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060613562458OnyKlDRcf02QGY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.14166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}